Grimaldi's Pizzeria is currently hiring Servers and Hosts/Hostesses for our Gilbert, AZ location at San Tan. <br>
<br>
 We recruit, hire, and train strong, self-disciplined people who are committed to our concept and "family" environment.<br>
 If you have positive energy and have a passion for pizza, we would like you to consider becoming a part of the Grimaldi's family.<br>
<br>
 Requirements:<br>
 Experience working in a restaurant environment a plus<br>
 FOH experience a plus<br>
 Enjoy working with people <br>
 Self-motivated and highly-energetic with a great attitude<br>
 Great communication skills<br>
 Ability to stand for long periods of time<br>
 <br>
Responsibilities of Server:<br>
 Ensure complete customer satisfaction<br>
 Knowledge of menu and wine list <br>
 Must possess Food Handler's Card<br>
 General restaurant preparation <br>
 Maintains a sanitary environment<br>
 Works well in a fast paced environment <br>
<br>
 Paste the below link into your browser to apply for the Server position:<br>
<a href="https://grimaldispizzeria.clearcompany.com/careers/jobs/be30c260-8776-3162-0326-2f45bb0cc60e/apply?source=461547-CS-12672" rel="nofollow">https://grimaldispizzeria.clearcompany.com/careers/jobs/be30c260-8776-3162-0326-2f45bb0cc60e/apply?source=461547-CS-12672</a><br>
<br>
Responsibilities of Hosts/Hostesses:<br>
 Greets and seats guests at the main entrance<br>
 Answers phones in accordance with Company standards.<br>
 Takes reservations and controls the flow of seating and waiting times<br>
 General restaurant preparation<br>
 Maintains a sanitary environment<br>
 Works well in a fast paced environment <br>
<br>
 Please click the below link to apply for the Host/Hostess position:<br>
<a href="https://grimaldispizzeria.clearcompany.com/careers/jobs/c4c6bca9-e32e-860c-f27e-8c0d01d73b17/apply?source=461546-CS-12672" rel="nofollow">https://grimaldispizzeria.clearcompany.com/careers/jobs/c4c6bca9-e32e-860c-f27e-8c0d01d73b17/apply?source=461546-CS-12672</a><br>
<br>
 OR TO SEE ALL AVAILABLE POSITIONS:<br>
<br>
 Visit our careers website at: <a href="https://www.grimaldispizzeria.com/careers" rel="nofollow">https://www.grimaldispizzeria.com/careers</a> <br>
<br>
 We are an equal opportunity employer <br>
 We E-verify    </section>

